            "title": "How are points earned?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>Customers earn points with every dollar spent. In the White Belt level, they’ll earn 1 point for $1 spent. The rate increases as customers move up reward levels. For Black Belt, they’ll earn 5 points for every $1 spent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_wwgRkt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What products earn points, and what products can points be redeemed for?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p><strong>You earn points on</strong>: DTF transfers, PermaStickers™, and DTF supplies. You do not earn points on Blanks, Patches, or Printhouse. </p><p><strong>You can use points to purchase</strong>: DTF transfers, PermaStickers™, DTF supplies and Blanks. You are unable to use points on Patches and Printhouse</p>"
