            "subtitle": "",
            "icon": "no-icon",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "body": "<p>As a member of Ninja Rewards, your reward level is determined by your total spend on orders over a rolling 12-month period. This means we continuously monitor your spending from the past 12 months and place you in the level that corresponds to that total.</p><p><strong>Here’s how it works:</strong></p><ul><li>White Belt: $0 - $249</li><li>Yellow Belt: $250 - $999</li><li>Blue Belt: $1,000 - $3,999</li><li>Black Belt: &gt; $4,000</li></ul>"
